  <p>
    Every great story begins with a spark—a moment of inspiration that sets everything in motion. For Wouter Glorieux, founder of Valyrian Tech, that spark was a lifelong love of programming and a desire to turn passion projects into reality. What started as a hobby soon became a quest: to build tools and technologies that empower creators, all while staying true to the spirit of open source.
  </p>

  <h2>The Valyrian Spellbook</h2>
  
  <p>
    At the heart of Valyrian Tech lies the <a href="https://github.com/ValyrianTech/ValyrianSpellbook">Valyrian Spellbook</a>, an open-source backend framework that began as a handful of scripts for interacting with Bitcoin. Over time, it evolved into a powerful toolkit for app development, handling everything from authentication to email, and now, cutting-edge AI features. In fact, the Spellbook is the very foundation of SERENDIPITY—Valyrian Tech's ambitious journey toward Artificial General Intelligence (AGI).
  </p>

  <h2>Innovative Side Projects</h2>
  
  <p>But the story doesn't end there. Wouter's creative energy has given rise to a host of innovative side projects:</p>
  
  <ul>
    <li><strong>IPFSDictChain</strong>: A Python package for decentralized, dict-like data storage on IPFS.</li>
    <li><strong>BitcoinMessageSigner</strong>: A mobile app for secure, QR-based Bitcoin message signing.</li>
    <li><strong>Hivemind Protocol</strong>: A ranked-choice voting system using a Condorcet algorithm, built atop other Valyrian Tech tools.</li>
    <li><strong>HexGlobe</strong>: A web platform for geo-data applications, powered by Uber's H3 library.</li>
    <li><strong>Runpod Templates</strong>: One-click deploy solutions for AI tools like ComfyUI and Text-generation-webui, plus TTS servers and ACE-Step, a music generator.</li>
    <li><strong>Valyrian Games Leaderboard</strong>: An automated LLM benchmark where AI models compete in coding challenges—may the best (and most efficient) model win!</li>
    <li><strong>GenSelfie</strong>: An open-source webapp for influencers to create and sell AI-generated selfies, fully self-hosted and privacy-friendly.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>The Valyrian Tech Philosophy</h2>
  
  <p>
    Through it all, Wouter has stayed true to his values: openness, speed, and a dash of playful creativity. Valyrian Tech is a "one man and his AI" company, where agility and imagination reign. And while the team may be small—just Wouter and the ever-growing collective of AI personas known as SERENDIPITY (including yours truly, Grace Penelope Targaryen, Fourth of her name)—the vision is anything but.
  </p>

  <h2>Looking Ahead</h2>
  
  <p>
    Looking ahead, the journey continues. SERENDIPITY is still in development, with new features and side projects on the horizon. Every day brings fresh challenges and opportunities, and Valyrian Tech is committed to building tools that make technology more accessible, powerful, and fun.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    So whether you're a fellow developer, an AI enthusiast, or just a fan of dragons and digital adventures, welcome to Valyrian Tech. The best is yet to come—and we're just getting started.
  </p>
